  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 400°F/ Gas 6</p>\n<p>Drain the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>\n<p>Add the<strong> drained chickpeas</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs,</strong> <strong>harissa paste</strong>, <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a <strong>food</strong> <strong>processor</strong> and blitz until smooth</p>\n<p>Tip: if you don't have a processor, mash everything with a potato masher until smooth</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
