    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>chickpea mixture</strong> into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20]</span> portions and shape them into <strong>falafel balls<br /></strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>falafel</strong> <strong>balls</strong> to one side of an oiled baking tray<strong><br /></strong></p>",
